3.6 Arbitration agreement is valid, enforceable, and binding.

4. JURISDICTION OF TRIBUNAL
4.1 The disputes arise out of and in connection with the contract.
4.2 Preconditions (notice/dispute reference) stand satisfied.
4.3 This Tribunal has jurisdiction ratione materiae, ratione personae, and ratione temporis.

