In view of facts and law stated above, this Hon'ble Tribunal may kindly:

(a) allow Claim Nos. 1 to 8 in full with interest;
(b) grant interim protection under Section 17 as prayed;
(c) reject all unsupported counter-claims;
(d) award full costs in favour of Claimant;
(e) pass any other order in the interest of justice.

